{"tid":1262430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"緊記！記者其實係人民嘅保護盾！","createTime":"2019-06-27T16:33:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T02:51:29.000Z","uid":70403,"like":96,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"54f9f27f8ac6c7fec83db51ccc8c8a069add7bec","tid":1262430,"uid":70403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:33:28.000Z","msg":"<strong>我明白有啲保護盾係親中親共，TVB會偏袒政府報道。緊急關頭，有前線記者在場拍攝可以令到警方比較克制。<br />\n<br />\n如果我地親手打爛個盾，到時警方會更加猖狂攻擊市民。無錯，TVB報道係誤導市民。不過，TVB前線記者同時間都保護現場安全。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">人民和記者不能被分化</div></span></span><br />\n無論報導有冇誤導性，一俾人影到市民主動攻擊前線記者已經係蝕章。大眾嘅焦點已經放係市民攻擊記者，唔係啲誤導報導。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">集中火力傳媒高層<br />\n唔好誤傷前線記者</div></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n！！！攻擊前線記者係完全冇用嘅行為！！！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1.對家或者TVB高層一定會大造文章<br />\n2.淡化咗警犬同記者嘅敵對關係<br />\n3.大眾只關注市民攻擊記者，失去誤導性報道嘅重點<br />\n4.前線記者和市民互相尊重嘅關係會被破裂<br />\n5.更少記者，更少鏡頭監察警方<br />\n6.<span style=\"color: red;\">直接搞尻前線記者對事情真係有幫助？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">集中咗警犬先，要搞都搞傳媒高層<br />\n傳媒高層決定咩嘢先可以出街</span></span><br />\n<br />\n記者係抗爭入面好重要，唔好直接搞尻佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw 現場舉牌，探下高層表達訴求，收集過往偏頗報道去TVB廠仲好過搞尻前線記者</strong>"},{"pid":"acedf46b89593cd556518160cd18b08e9fa875fd","tid":1262430,"uid":201237,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:35:50.000Z","msg":"係隔離屌兩野同舉吓牌好啦， 唔好阻佢地採訪"},{"pid":"182e5844565d564327ac300163852253a6daeeb0","tid":1262430,"uid":70403,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"acedf46b89593cd556518160cd18b08e9fa875fd","tid":1262430,"uid":201237,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:35:50.000Z","msg":"係隔離屌兩野同舉吓牌好啦， 唔好阻佢地採訪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:37:56.000Z","msg":"搞尻人地又蝕章又送咗子彈俾tvb高層射我地"},{"pid":"724624e2f5e6cf27727f772a9a7c832f1b17565d","tid":1262430,"uid":30743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:40:02.000Z","msg":"共產黨統戰再鍾意分化，<br />\n<br />\n所以cctvb一定要充分加以利用， <br />\n<br />\n發揮最大功能，向政府還以顏色"},{"pid":"23a5c58f571266329c1c3ec7fe47758b5a292a78","tid":1262430,"uid":30743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"182e5844565d564327ac300163852253a6daeeb0","tid":1262430,"uid":70403,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"acedf46b89593cd556518160cd18b08e9fa875fd","tid":1262430,"uid":201237,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:35:50.000Z","msg":"係隔離屌兩野同舉吓牌好啦， 唔好阻佢地採訪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:37:56.000Z","msg":"搞尻人地又蝕章又送咗子彈俾tvb高層射我地"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:40:56.000Z","msg":"咁就係，俾d畫面佢地loop足24小時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e7615df8f2ccadafd5155b212c9b4a8b8cf3683","tid":1262430,"uid":70403,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"724624e2f5e6cf27727f772a9a7c832f1b175